Dear Granma

Its a lily cheesy, you may be thinking what in carnation!?, but thistle be good. I beleaf its time to put the petal to the metal once and floral. Just pollen your leg, no bud omen here, its not really once and floral, actually its the opposiete. Its just thyme I rose to the occasion after the many oopsie daisy days, so if its bouquet with you I have you clovered on the floral front for the next 12 months.

Love, David
